<dt>Art Sale</dt>
<dd><strong>Apr 23 Sat &middot; 10:00 am - 4:00 pm</strong>
<br>We accept prints, posters, oils, pastels, as well as fine jewelry, ceramics, and other art pieces. 
<br>Those who donate art will receive a tax receipt for the price raised at the Art Sale. If you have art to donate please call Sheila 780-481-0056 for pick up or drop off your art at the Church office during regular office hours. If you have any questions please give Sheila a telephone call.
</dd>


<dt>Rummage Sale</dt>
<dd><strong>Apr 22 Fri &middot; 5:00 - 8:00 pm
<br>Apr 30 Sat &middot; 8:30 am - 3:00 pm</strong>
<br>Our spring rummage sale is fast approaching. It is an important event which benefits our community. The sale proceeds go to R-W's general revenue, which is used to keep our church operating. The "leftovers" benefit both the Bissell Centre and the Canadian Diabetes Association. 
<br>We would appreciate you bringing your donations (excluding furniture please), on Wednesday April 27th and Thursday April 28th from 9 am to 8 pm.
<br>For full details visit the <a href="http://www.rwuc.org/rummage.html">Rummage Sale webpage</a></dd>
</dd>



