<dt>Soul OUTing</dt>
<dd><strong>Sunday, June 14 &middot; 7:00 pm, Chapel</strong>
<br>A safe place where LGBT persons and allies can explore the sacred and connect with one another, this informal experience is part worship, part sharing circle, part bible study.
<br><strong>Sunday, June 14 &middot; 4:00 pm - 7:00 pm, Club Room</strong> 
<br>One of our artists in residents, Chaka will also be showcasing masks that have been created throughout the spring season in collaboration with Soul OUTing.  
Masks will be exhibited along with autobiographical narratives of the people behind the mask.
<br>Full details are on the <a href="http://www.rwuc.org/affirming.html">affirming</a> web page.</dd>


